Author: jl777c#5810
Content: pushed support for -ac_script, which sets the -ac_perc vout[1] to be the specified script, the -ac_pubkey is ignored if -ac_script is set

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: this will allow founders reward or block tx percentage to go to CC vout

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: you would need to get the scriptPubKey of the CC vout by making one on another CC chain first, then use the hex of it

Author: jl777c#5810
Content: this also allows -ac_perc vout[1] to go to multisig addresses
